{
  "id": "RAW_d179d0",
  "title": "前端开发又幸福了，Cursor + Figma MCP 快速还原设计稿",
  "url": "https://juejin.cn/post/7480183580120055819",
  "date": "2025-03-11 06:31:12",
  "author": "代码小学僧",
  "siteName": "掘金本周最热",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body cache result\">\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-0\">前言</h2>\n   <p>昨天朋友发给我一个开源项目 <a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FGLips%2FFigma-Context-MCP\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/GLips/Figma-Context-MCP\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">github.com/GLips/Figma…</a> 是一个 Figma 的 MCP 服务。</p>\n   <p>MCP 是最近比较火的概念，你可能在推特经常能看到。我用自己的话理解，简单讲就是一个开放给 AI 应用访问外部某某平台，某某应用的一个接口，AI 可以通过 MCP 来获取到更具体的相关数据。</p>\n   <p>站内优秀文章更详细的可以看下这篇文章的介绍 <a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7478304240122134566\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7478304240122134566\">juejin.cn/post/747830…</a> (下图来源自互联网蛮形象的)</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ee5bc741702646bbb4ade0b6d9137269~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=uARwQpbGmoS8HBiN%2Fkg1CqEhpeI%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>Cursor 不用介绍了吧。大名鼎鼎的 AI IDE <a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cursor.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.cursor.com/\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Cursor 官网</a> 他支持绑定 MCP 服务，我使用的 0.45 版本，应该此版本以上都支持。在 Setting 中找到 MCP Server 进行添加配置。</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/f0a84b660cab4ddfb2f458a28db8f407~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=5%2BpJFE3RmSrxMMMzAeR5RJa6gpA%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>我直接使用了下这个 Figma MCP + Cursor 感觉很不错，感恩开源。下面介绍下使用教程。</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-1\">按照项目 Readme 操作</h2>\n   <p>在 Figma 点击头像然后进入 Setting 先创建一个 <code>Figma api-key</code>。</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8ac249559e2c4168b34825e5de99485e~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=8seKBWQ2maXe9TYoWO7sVcOQU4Q%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>给予一些权限。我这里给可读可写了。可自行修改。应该是至少需要 Dev resources 可读的。</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ff3d1cebd02f4eda95cec21459415b67~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=cAGaSFKAuYyGbQcepISDF2MDs8g%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>复制下来生成的 <code>api-key</code> 然后在终端执行命令。</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-shell code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"shell\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\">pnpx figma-developer-mcp --figma-api-key=&lt;your-figma-api-key&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>看到显示在本地 3333 端口启动服务了，就可以去 Cursor 链接了。</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/6459f085abad4c2997777218a12ba935~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=iXMm6SzyNYx3u7aCY755NrfSgg0%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>添加上亮小绿点就表示链接成功了。</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/efcd0e58b75840aa9a1e4461582cc165~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=mXisgmwPyuHnJpgIlKJEJN0QXC0%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"> <img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8369de49d3564d16ac45ebfb4021ec0a~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=OYysuYK5ktHtSaGwB8AT1XKZv14%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>在 Figma 复制选中的模块</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8903143a83a348778bbda20cb7e76872~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=aIk26YViQENDxQEEr9rvlQOnn84%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>指定要写入的文件，并提出相对应的要求。他就开始写了。（好像开启 agent 模式效果更佳，我直接使用的 nomal，朋友用 nomal 读取不到 Figma）</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8d14f258f1fa4e459dda017c2280ee59~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=u6yffOEWWZuR2eyOyEdrgVTPW34%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <p>最后的成品 下方是设计稿，上方是他一次性就实现的界面。还是很赞的，调整下高度和边距就可以用了。</p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/9eb360f3838c42dcbc5b69e18686de1c~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5Luj56CB5bCP5a2m5YOn:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1742282245&amp;x-signature=UHKcT%2FzwzHLL2M5sBWhi21iEqqc%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\">\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-tsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"tsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ReactECharts</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'echarts-for-react'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">LineChart</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> data = [</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周一'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">150</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周二'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">230</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周三'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">224</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周四'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">218</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周五'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">135</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周六'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">147</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">    { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">date</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'周日'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">260</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-nu